State of DeFi Q4 2024

Kinji Steimetz

Jan 17, 2025   5 min read

This report consolidates and examines the quarterly and month-over-month performances of leading DeFi applications. It comprehensively analyzes market capitalizations, TVLs, DEXs, lending protocols, perpetual DEXs, Liquid Staking Tokens (LSTs), stablecoins, and bridges.
